China 's fertility rate , which stood at four births per mother in <TIMEX3 tid="t37" type="DATE" value="1970">1970</TIMEX3> , was 1.82 in <TIMEX3 tid="t38" type="DATE" value="2000">2000</TIMEX3> .
\ * China 's 55 registered ethnic groups , aside from the majority Han Chinese , accounted for 8.49 percent of the population , up from 8.41 percent in <TIMEX3 tid="t39" type="DATE" value="2000">2000</TIMEX3> .
