In <TIMEX3 tid="t40" type="DATE" value="2010">2010</TIMEX3> , the number of people with a university education was 8,930 per 100,000 , almost 2.5 times more than in <TIMEX3 tid="t41" type="DATE" value="2000">2000</TIMEX3> , when it stood at 3,611 .
